            "body": "<p>// similar post:<\/p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3443858/c-sharp-var-keyword-equivalent-in-java\">C# var keyword equivalent in java?<\/a><\/p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>JEP - JDK Enhancement-Proposal<\/p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://openjdk.java.net/jeps/286\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">http://openjdk.java.net/jeps/286<\/a><\/p>\n\n<p>JEP 286: Local-Variable Type Inference<\/p>\n\n<p>Author Brian Goetz<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>// Goals:\nvar list = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;();  // infers ArrayList&lt;String&gt;\nvar stream = list.stream();          // infers Stream&lt;String&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
